(Death to Jume, come down and fight.  It's the final countdown!)

Unitron/Shockwave:




Unitron tried to dodge the shot, but it was futile, and a good portion of his 
side was blown apart and he was sent flying back a few feet, slamming to his 
back and going into a stasis lock type mode.

Emperor Shockwave had been watching the fight, and his engines roared to 
life, transforming in mid air and landing several feet away from Megatron.  
"So you are the robot taking claim to the name of Megatron?"
